When a technician is dispatched, Barbarosa should notify the homeowner by text, email, or in-app message.

The message should include:
- Technician name
- Company name
- Estimated arrival time
- Job/request type
- Optional technician photo
- Optional vehicle description
- Contact button
- Reschedule/request callback option

Example:

Your technician Michael from Bravo Water Heaters & Plumbing has been dispatched.

Estimated Arrival:
2:15 PM - 2:45 PM

Service:
Water Heater Inspection

You can reply to this message or open Barbarosa for updates.